HEADWORD: Tule
<hw>Tu"le</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Mex.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A large bulrush (<spn>Scirpus lacustris</spn>,
and <spn>Scirpus Tatora</spn>) growing abundantly on overflowed land in
California and elsewhere.</def>⟦br⟧
